# Win+Shift+Down move down
# Win+Shift+Up move up
# Win+Shift+Right move right

# alternatively, you can use the cursor keys:
# Win+Alt+Left move left
# Win+Alt+Down move down
# Win+Alt+Up move up
# Win+Alt+Right move right
